caption.p: (a) The protein levels of Bax measured by Western blot. “0” means diets with no MOL, “4” means diets supplemented with 4% MOL, and “8” means diets supplemented with 8% MOL. (b) The statistical analyses results of the Western blot of the protein level of Bax. Data are presented as mean ± SEM, n = 8. Results are normalized to β‐actin
